<bibRefCitation author="Sousa, J. R. P. &amp; Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Esposito, M. C." box="[938,1139,330,357]" pageId="107" pageNumber="108" pagination="1 - 10" refId="ref115413" refString="Sousa, J. R. P., Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Esposito, M. C. (2015) Distribution and abundance of necrophagous flies (Diptera: Calliphoridae and Sarcophagidae) in Maranhao, Northeastern Brazil. Journal of Insect Science, 15 (1), 1 - 10. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / jisesa / iev 054" type="journal article" year="2015">
Sousa 
<emphasis box="[1014,1072,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="107" pageNumber="108">et al.</emphasis>
2015
</bibRefCitation>
, 2016) and in a mangrove area (
<bibRefCitation author="Sousa, J. R. P. &amp; Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Juen, L. &amp; Esposito, M. C." box="[213,413,367,394]" pageId="107" pageNumber="108" pagination="0164826" refId="ref115484" refString="Sousa, J. R. P., Carvalho-Filho, F. S., Juen, L. &amp; Esposito, M. C. (2016) Evaluating the effects of different vegetation types on necrophagous fly communities (Diptera: Calliphoridae; Sarcophagidae): Implications for conservation. PLoS One, 11 (10), e 0164826, 1 - 23. https: // doi. org / 10.1371 / journal. pone. 0164826" type="journal article" year="2016">
Sousa 
<emphasis box="[288,345,367,393]" italics="true" pageId="107" pageNumber="108">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
