<bibRefCitation author="Sousa, J. R. P. &amp; Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Esposito, M. C." pageId="107" pageNumber="108" pagination="1 - 10" refId="ref115413" refString="Sousa, J. R. P., Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Esposito, M. C. (2015) Distribution and abundance of necrophagous flies (Diptera: Calliphoridae and Sarcophagidae) in Maranhao, Northeastern Brazil. Journal of Insect Science, 15 (1), 1 - 10. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / jisesa / iev 054" type="journal article" year="2015">
Sousa 
<emphasis box="[151,207,403,429]" italics="true" pageId="107" pageNumber="108">et al.</emphasis>
